label: Network Degradation Analysis
detail: The dataset for network degradation analysis across 5G cells in Oman.

label: Energy Disaggregation
description: All Appliances Energy Disaggregation in Saudi Arabia
detail: The dataset for energy disaggregation with appliances is designed to facilitate the study and development of algorithms aimed at identifying individual appliance energy usage from aggregate energy consumption data in a household or commercial setting. This type of dataset typically includes high-resolution energy usage data recorded over time, broken down by individual appliances such as refrigerators, air conditioners, washing machines, and others. The data may be collected using smart meters or dedicated energy monitoring devices installed on each appliance or electrical circuit.

label: San Francisco Elevation Contour
description: Elevation contours of San Francisco mainland and Treasure Island/Yerba Island.
detail: This dataset contains elevation contours for San Francisco mainland and Treasure Island/Yerba Island. Based on San Francisco Elevation Datum. Data source: [DataSF](https://data.sfgov.org/City-Infrastructure/Street-Tree-List/tkzw-k3nq/data).

label: San Francisco Street Tree Map
description: A 3d hexbin density map showing every single streets in San Francisco
detail: This dataset contains a list of dpw maintained street trees including planting date, species and location. Data source: [DataSF](https://data.sfgov.org/City-Infrastructure/Street-Tree-List/tkzw-k3nq/data).

label: 2017 Unemployment Rates for U.S. Counties
description: 2017 Labor force information for U.S. Counties
detail: This dataset contains 2017 labor force information from the [Bureau of Labor Statistics](https://www.bls.gov/lau/#tables) joined with county shapefiles from the [Census Bureau](https://www.census.gov/geo/maps-data/data/cbf/cbf_counties.html).
